 KADOKAWA Game Linkage 格斗游戏专门 VTuber 团体“Reasaru Plan”公布https://www.moguravr.com/kadokawa-game-linkage-vtuber/MoguLive編集部 Fri, 26 Jan 2024 06:39:44 +0000VTuber https://www.moguravr.com/?p=244665 <p>角川游戏联动株式会社宣布成立专门从事格斗游戏的 VTuber 团体“Resaru Plan”。 “Resaru Plan”是一个以“充分享受格斗游戏并传达其魅力”为理念的团体。</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/kadokawa-game-linkage-vtuber/">角川游戏联动的格斗游戏专业VTuber团体“Resaru Plan”宣布的帖子</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上出现。</p> ; <p>角川游戏联动株式会社宣布成立专门从事格斗游戏的 VTuber 团体“ <a href="https://twitter.com/lethalplan" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Resaru Plan</a> ”。<br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6c0a2796861f9edba385d81367653da5-kix.nli3sc4gmyb2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6c0a2796861f9edba385d81367653da5-kix.nli3sc4gmyb2-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6c0a2796861f9edba385d81367653da5-kix.nli3sc4gmyb2-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6c0a2796861f9edba385d81367653da5-kix.nli3sc4gmyb2-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6c0a2796861f9edba385d81367653da5-kix.nli3sc4gmyb2-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6c0a2796861f9edba385d81367653da5-kix.nli3sc4gmyb2-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6c0a2796861f9edba385d81367653da5-kix.nli3sc4gmyb2-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> “Reasu Plan”是格斗游戏VTuber团体的项目，其运营理念是“充分享受格斗游戏并传达其魅力”。据介绍，作为经销商，他将从事免费、有趣、认真的格斗游戏活动，活跃格斗游戏行业乃至整个游戏行业。</p><p>成员有星鸟友守、雨鸟长树、千奈美宗林三人。未来他会积极参加各种线上活动，包括各种游戏锦标赛。</p><h2> VTuber简介</h2><h3>星鸟智</h3><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6c0a2796861f9edba385d81367653da5-kix.qfgfcsx3vr4m-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6c0a